{"tid":2109072,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"料飲食業本月生意額損失30億 黃家和冀政府支援","createTime":"2020-07-15T03:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T07:54:27.000Z","uid":166845,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4fa414fd964b491112523f79377cc7596de5bc0d","tid":2109072,"uid":166845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T03:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/9f286f601226e255c04b1ad6f9dea372/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200714/_2020071410182347760.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F9f286f601226e255c04b1ad6f9dea372%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200714%2F_2020071410182347760.jpg&h=c6875112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府昨晚宣布由明天(15日)起再次收緊防疫措施，為限制人流聚集，食肆將由晚上6時至早上5時禁止堂食。香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和預料超過大半食肆會有困難，今月生意額將損失30億元。<br />\n<br />\n黃家和表示，措施突如其來，並非每間食肆都有條件外賣，例如婚宴及宴會場所、火鍋店等，可能會選擇索性暫時停業，即使茶餐廳可外賣，亦難以彌補堂食生意的損失，外賣配送又牽涉人問題，難以同時應付全港食肆，若外賣自取，可能又違反限聚令，食肆只准外賣要面對很大問題，希望政府考慮如何支援業界。<br />\n<br />\n他估計，單計7月份餐飲業可能會損失約30億元生意，若措施持續，之後每個月的損失會更大。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1818826/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%E6%96%99%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E9%A1%8D%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B130%E5%84%84%E9%BB%83%E5%AE%B6%E5%92%8C%E5%86%80%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1818826%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F%25E9%25A1%258D%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B130%25E5%2584%2584%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%2586%2580%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=2059f0a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%